title: Bob Dole's Last Interview
description: We're re-releasing last month's interview with American hero, Bob Dole. Listen as he describes his proudest moment and offers his thoughts on the future of our country. There will never be another like him. Rest in peace, Sir.
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Bob Dole, Josh Holmes, Michael Duncan, Comfortably Smug, John Ashbrook)
